reviews.review_text:
The best source for this show Spring '87 in all its glory, but not too many sources to choose from. Even the Charlie Miller 'SBD' won't do here. The AUDs that have been downloaded a lot previously don't come close to this. Two sound like there is a lot of distance between the mics and the stage, and one is very tinny. This source has the clearest instrument/vocal levels and most subdued audience. 

Garcia's vocals are priceless during this tour. His range is so much better than it was during the '88-'90 era. Just listen to Althea.
